Texts.Eng: A console for communicating with S.A.I.L..
Texts.Chs: 与S.A.I.L.通信的控制台。。

Texts.Eng: A station for interacting with S.A.I.L..
Texts.Chs: 与S.A.I.L.互动的站点。。

Texts.Eng: A tech station - S.A.I.L displays data in both 'visible' and infrared light best suited for Peglaci eyes.
Texts.Chs: 一个科技站-S.A.I.L用最适合企鹅族眼睛的可见光和红外光显示数据。

Texts.Eng: Detected S.A.I.L. interface. Console enables communication with S.A.I.L..
Texts.Chs: 检测到S.A.I.L.接口。控制台支持与S.A.I.L.的通信。。
地球遭到了不明力量的攻击，星球结构被彻底摧毁。
Texts.Eng: Earth was attacked by an unknown force, and was subsequently annihilated.

Texts.Chs: 叶族人修修修好了这个面板，唤醒了飞船！
Texts.Eng: Floran fix thisss panel to wake ship up!
Floran use thisss magic panel to talk to S.A.I.L.!
Texts.Chs: 叶族人用这个魔法面板和S.A.I.L.说话。！
您好.操作者.我是S.A.I.L, 您的舰载人工智能模块.我负责管理您的飞船的维护事项。
Texts.Eng: I am S.A.I.L, your Ship-based Artificial Intelligence Lattice. I manage the maintainance of your ship.

Texts.Chs: 我的程序也被设定为能够给您提供信息和建议。
Texts.Eng: I am also programmed to offer you information and advice.

Texts.Chs: 我可以在这里弄一弄我的科技，也可以与SAIL交谈。
Texts.Eng: I can mess with my techs here, as well as talk to the AI, S.A.I.L.
I can speak to S.A.I.L. using this console. It's good to have another AI on the ship.
Texts.Chs: 我可以用这个控制台和S.A.I.L.通话。船上有另一台人工智能真好。
我能通过这个面板和SAIL进行交流。
Texts.Eng: I can talk to SAIL through this console.
I can use this station to talk to S.A.I.L..
Texts.Chs: 我可以利用这个电台和S.A.I.L.通话。。

Texts.Eng: I can use this to load up on augs or chat with S.A.I.L., if I get lonely.
Texts.Chs: 如果我感到孤独的话，我可以用它来加载augs或与S.A.I.L聊天。
我首先需要重启这个设施，然后与SAIL进行交流。
Texts.Eng: I first need to reboot this station to communicate with SAIL.

Texts.Chs: 如果我能重启这个设施，SAIL应该就能回到在线状态了！
Texts.Eng: If I can reboot this station SAIL should come back online!
Interface-S.A.I.L.. Akki talk to ship here.
Texts.Chs: 接口-S.A.I.L。。Akki在这里和船通话。

Texts.Eng: My friend.
Texts.Chs: 我的朋友。
请重启系统。
Texts.Eng: Please reboot the system.

Texts.Chs: 重启系统失败。
Texts.Eng: Reboot process remains uninitiated.

Texts.Chs: 重启系统可以将您与飞船的交互度提高到73%。
Texts.Eng: Rebooting has shown to improve ship interaction satisfaction levels by 73%.

Texts.Chs: 系统重启需要经由一名有意识的智慧实体与S.A.I.L控制台交汇互动才能进行。
Texts.Eng: Rebooting requires a conscious entity to interact with the S.A.I.L console.

Texts.Chs: 重启这个设施后，SAIL应该就能与我交谈了。
Texts.Eng: Rebooting this station should enable me to talk to SAIL.

Texts.Chs: 系统重启中...
Texts.Eng: Rebooting...

Texts.Chs: S.A.I.L 控制面板
Texts.Eng: S.A.I.L Interface
S.A.I.L. is one companion who will never fail you.
Texts.Chs: S.A.I.L.是一个永远不会让你失望的伴侣。

舰载人工智能模块，简称S.A.I.L。
^#B8860B;可在飞船用家具定制台调整种族风格^reset;
Texts.Eng: Ship-based Artificial Intelligence Lattice, or S.A.I.L for short.

Texts.Chs: 系统已崩溃，请重新启动。
Texts.Eng: System is down, please reboot.

Texts.Chs: 科技站
Texts.Eng: Tech Station
The Nomada doesn't like AIs like S.A.I.L., but the Protectorate insisted on installing it.
Texts.Chs: Momada不像S.A.I.L.那样喜欢人工智能，但大地守护团坚持要安装它。
飞船在脱离地球轨道过程中导航系统受到严重损害。我们当前所处的位置不明。
Texts.Eng: The ship's navigation systems were damaged in our escape. Our location is currently unknown.
This console allows for interaction with S.A.I.L.. It's nice to have someone to talk to.
Texts.Chs: 此控制台允许与S.A.I.L.进行交互。。有人聊天真好。

Texts.Eng: This console allows me to communicate with S.A.I.L..
Texts.Chs: 此控制台允许我与S.A.I.L.进行通信。。
这个控制台将会允许我与SAIL进行交流。我首先需要重启它。
Texts.Eng: This console will allow me to communicate with SAIL. I need to reboot it first.
This here station lets me talk with S.A.I.L..
Texts.Chs: 这个站点让我和S.A.I.L.通话。。

Texts.Eng: This panel allows for interaction with S.A.I.L., the ship-based AI.
Texts.Chs: 该面板允许与基于船舶的人工智能S.A.I.L.进行交互。

Texts.Eng: This reminds me of the One.
Texts.Chs: 这让我想起了唯一者。

Texts.Eng: This station allows me to communicate with S.A.I.L..
Texts.Chs: 该站允许我与S.A.I.L.通信。。

Texts.Eng: This station allows me to talk to S.A.I.L..
Texts.Chs: 这个站台允许我和S.A.I.L.通话。。
重启它，我就可以和SAIL进行对话了。
Texts.Eng: Time to reboot this station so I can talk to SAIL.

Texts.Chs: 要想使用你的S.A.I.L，请重启系统。
Texts.Eng: To make use of your S.A.I.L please reboot.

Texts.Chs: 当它工作时，我就可以通过这个控制台与SAIL交谈。
Texts.Eng: When it's working, I can talk to SAIL through this console.
